    "body": "Note how it doesn't think OpenSSL is installed. This seems like a quirk (not quite a bug, but I don't think it was intended either):\r\n```\r\n[+]  glayfkq          ^curl@7.50.3%gcc@4.9.3 arch=linux-centos7-x86_64\r\n[-]  nhr6nvf              ^openssl@system%gcc@4.9.3 arch=linux-centos7-x86_64\r\n[+]  gs5rqbz          ^expat@2.2.0%gcc@4.9.3 arch=linux-centos7-x86_64\r\n```\r\n`openssl` is set up in my `packages.yaml`:\r\n```\r\n    openssl:\r\n        paths:\r\n            openssl@system: /false/path\r\n        version: [system]\r\n        buildable: False\r\n```\r\n",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
